title: Youji Shijie
description: Youji Shijie 有機世界 or Organic World is an organic and vegetarian store and snack bar. If you are looking for organic veggies, ask to go to the back where a wall of fridges contain an impressive supply for organic restaurants in the area. Ma Taitai runs the store and also provides weekend classes on the latest juicers, dehydrators, bread makers and other European health conscious machines that she sells here. Chinese address: 東榮路.
